  "description": "Two obsidian blades, one angled 12 degrees from the other — their resonant frequencies almost but not quite aligned. The beat frequency between them produces slow tremolo when held, rapid shimmer when played staccato. Cross-mod depth set so each blade feeds the other's filter. Neither can sound without referencing the other.",
